{"name":"usermod","desc":"`usermod` 命令行工具可用于修改现有用户的属性、权限和组成员资格。","usages":[{"form":{"":{"name":"用户名","required":true,"type":"string"},"-a":{"type":"string","name":"在用户的现有组之外追加组成员资格","optionName":"-a"},"-b":{"type":"check","name":"在用户主目录中创建新的基本目录","optionName":"-b"},"-c":{"type":"string","name":"用户的注释","optionName":"-c"},"-d":{"type":"string","name":"用户的主目录","optionName":"-d"},"-e":{"type":"check","name":"用户帐户的有效期限","optionName":"-e"},"-f":{"type":"check","name":"忽略 /etc/default/useradd 文件中的值","optionName":"-f"},"-g":{"type":"string","name":"用户的初始登录组","optionName":"-g"},"-G":{"type":"string","name":"用户的附加组列表","optionName":"-G"},"-h":{"type":"check","name":"显示帮助文本","optionName":"-h"},"-l":{"type":"string","name":"新用户名","optionName":"-l"},"-L":{"type":"check","name":"锁定用户的密码","optionName":"-L"},"-m":{"type":"check","name":"在用户的主目录中创建新的基本目录","optionName":"-m"},"-o":{"type":"check","name":"允许使用非唯一的用户 ID","optionName":"-o"},"-p":{"type":"string","name":"用户的加密密码","optionName":"-p"},"-s":{"type":"string","name":"用户的 shell","optionName":"-s"},"-u":{"type":"string","name":"用户 ID","optionName":"-u"},"-U":{"type":"check","name":"解锁用户的密码","optionName":"-U"},"-Z":{"type":"string","name":"设置 SELinux 用户映射的 SELinux 用户","optionName":"-Z"}}}],"content":"<h2 id=\"例子\">例子</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>将用户 <code>jdoe</code> 添加到组 <code>sales</code>：<code>sudo usermod -a -G sales jdoe</code></li>\n<li>将用户 <code>jdoe</code> 的主目录更改为 <code>/home/jdoe-new</code>：<code>sudo usermod -d /home/jdoe-new jdoe</code></li>\n<li>更改用户 <code>jdoe</code> 的注释信息为 <code>&quot;John Doe, Engineering&quot;</code>：<code>sudo usermod -c &quot;John Doe, Engineering&quot; jdoe</code></li>\n<li>更改用户 <code>jdoe</code> 的默认 shell 为 <code>zsh</code>：<code>sudo usermod -s /bin/zsh jdoe</code></li>\n<li>更改用户 <code>jdoe</code> 的 UID 为 <code>1001</code>：<code>sudo usermod -u 1001 jdoe</code></li>\n</ul>\n"}